room_title: Escape room "DaVinci's Challenge" by Kryptology Escape Rooms in Pigeon Forge
room_description: You and a group of archeology students are on an expedition in Florence Italy. While exploring some empty buildings in an old part of the city, you find a hidden door. Inside your team makes what could be the biggest discovery of the century: Leonardo Da Vinci's lost workshop. Unfortunately, the door has locked behind you. Can you follow the clues left by Da Vinci himself to find your way out?
